messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
Say, listen, do you realize you’re
breaking hearts by being successful?It’s your fault that Team Galactic
members are in so much pain...
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
See? You’ve left me brokenhearted,
too...
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
Someone’s joy is another person’s
sorrow...Everyone be happy and laughing?
How ridiculous!Team Galactic should be doing all the
laughing!
